主持人問到：「咁無商無量係咪要佔領？」時回答：「係嘞！」[23]，自此被一些網民戲為「佔領之母」，為日後的佔領抗爭樹立不凡的榜樣，而其粗暴的言論則受到不少批評。[24]<br />\n<br />\n蔣麗芸稱，「成個船啲人係希望去下龍灣，到咗下龍灣哪就落唔到船，上唔到岸，大家就好失望，但係大家亦都覺得船公司又好，旅行社又好，都未畀到一個滿意嘅答覆。（整艘船上的人是希望去下龍灣，抵達後卻上不了岸，大家就很失望，但是大家都覺得無論船公司還是旅行社，都未給到一個滿意的答覆）」（她在2014年與家人乘郵輪到越南，但未能到下龍灣上岸遊覽。）[25]"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T09:57:23.000Z","msg":"佔領之母<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"510aba84905026692c53adacb7b4928f208fb724","tid":1247353,"uid":64953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T09:58:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db8f3d526853e8177b18c5e540b2aac7540c0bbb","tid":1247353,"uid":53369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T09:59:53.000Z","msg":"泛民記者會啱啱讚元秋誠實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又可以出圖話佢已經叛變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59858566616414ea737bf3554955f07084463abc","tid":1247353,"uid":182984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T09:59:58.000Z","msg":"大推"},{"pid":"a1269bb95f9468e087109e57ba0c159a7a909c36","tid":1247353,"uid":73621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T10:02:34.000Z","msg":"內部人都大屌佢！"},{"pid":"c3cab51d715d143296acc2865b05d16b1f713a53","tid":1247353,"uid":10249,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T10:02:46.000Z","msg":"都要搞埋民建聯啦 <br />\n<br />\n蔣麗雲忠言逆耳 民建聯竟出賣撐送中選民 區會立會票債票償！ 寧投白票也不投民建聯！"},{"pid":"cfe33fd458225db6a9db79c0265a392c3a91fa8e","tid":1247353,"uid":72875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T10:14:20.000Z","msg":"Android機有無辦法share俾d廢老？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b39ff9832573b1912afc4b65f21b235ffb785c6","tid":1247353,"uid":22959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T1